Titiyu ya William Samuelson na tate yae
Onthue ankho tukala mongalandya koutundilo yo Dakota do Sul .
Okuundapa mongalandya ankho otyipuka tyimwe ombunga yetu ilinga unene , mahi ankho hatyoko tyakolela vali unene .
Ovo tate vambatisalwa avakala Onombangi mba Jeova mo 1934 .
Tate yange Clarence , na Alfred titiyu yange , vakalele ovakuatesiko vewaneno ( pehepano ñgeno vaihanwa okuti ononkhalamutwe mbo vakulu vewaneno ) kewaneno limwe etutu ko Conde okumbili kwo Dakota .
Ame nomphange yange Dorothy , tuakala ovaivisi Vouhamba etyi ankho tuna omanima epandu .
O William Samuelson mo 1952
Ovionge vio nonthiki ononthatu no vio nthiki ike ankho otyipuka tyakolela momuenyo wetu .
Ombimbiliya yati : “ Una weenda no vanandunge , nae makala nonondunge , ” iya mombunga yetu ankho muna ovanthu ovanyingi ovanongo vankhuatesako okukala omukokoli - ndyila .
Pakala vala katutu Dorothy nae akala omukokoli - ndyila .
